reviewText: OK as far as it goes, but the attempt to make a "surreal" video with just music support is a bit of a disappointment,  The photography is fine, but this could have been been so much better with just a bit of narration. The viewer is left wondering what they are looking at.  Also, while the scenery is great, some (just a few) shots of modern day Alaska (cities, sports,  fishing, industries, cultural activities) would have made a much better video for sharing.  Alaska is NOT just scenery.
